<placeName cert="high">Theadelphia</placeName>
<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">PThead21</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Αὐρηλίῳ Ὀλυμπίῳ πραιποσίτῳ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πά</supplied>γ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ου</unclear> <num value="8"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">η</unclear></num> 

    <lb n="2"/>παρὰ Αὐρηλίου Σακαῶνος Σαταβοῦτος ἀπὸ κώ-

    <lb n="3"/>μης Θεαδελφίας. μισθωτ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">οῦ</unclear> μου τυγχά-

    <lb n="4"/>νοντος θρεμμάτων Ῥούφου ἀπὸ πριμιπιλα-

    <lb n="5"/>ρίων καὶ τούτων βοσκομένων ἐν πεδίῳ Βερνι-

    <lb n="6"/>κίδο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> Αἰγιαλοῦ τοῦ ὑπὸ σὲ πά<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γο</unclear>υ, οὐκ οἶδ᾽ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὅπ</unclear>ως 

    <lb n="7"/>κατὰ τὸν Θὼθ <add place="supralinear">μῆνα</add> τινὲς κακοῦργοι ἐπιστάντες 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐκεῖσε διὰ νυκτὸς ἔνθα τὰ θρέμματα 

    <lb n="9"/>ἐβόσκετο καὶ ἀπεσύλησαν ἐξ α<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὐτ</unclear>ῶν 

    <lb n="10"/>αἶγας τὸν ἀριθμὸν δέκα ἕξ <num value="16"/>. ἐμοῦ τοίνυν πολυ-

    <lb n="11"/>πραγμονοῦντος κατελαβόμην Πέτρον υἱὸν Μαρίας 

    <lb n="12"/>οἰκοῦντα ἐν ἐποικίῳ Πτολεμαίου καὶ Ἰσίδωρ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ον</supplied> τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὸν</unclear> 


    <lb n="13"/>ἀπὸ ἐποικίο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υ</unclear> Μύρωνος καὶ <expan>α<ex cert="high">ὐτὸν</ex></expan> <choice><corr>ὡς</corr><sic>ος</sic></choice> ξένον οἰκοῦντα 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐν τῷ αὐτῷ ἐποικίῳ <choice><corr>Πτολεμαίου</corr><sic>πτολεμαιω</sic></choice> τοῦτο <add place="supralinear">ὑπ᾽ α<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὐτῶν</unclear></add> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">πεπ</unclear>λη-

    <lb n="15"/>μελῆσθαι. ἀναγκαίως <choice><corr>ἀνόσιον</corr><sic>ανοσιω</sic></choice> <choice><corr>πρᾶγμα</corr><sic>πρα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μμ</unclear>α</sic></choice> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὀ</unclear>δυρόμε-

    <lb n="16"/>νος ἐπιδίδωμί σοι τάδε τὰ βιβλία, αὐτὰ ταῦτα μαρτυρό-

    <lb n="17"/>μενος, ἀξ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>ῶν τούτους μετακαλέσασθαί σε 

    <lb n="18"/>καὶ πρῶτον μὲν ἅπερ ἀπεσύλησαν ἀποκαταστα-

    <lb n="19"/>θῆναί μοι ποιήσῃς, <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἔ</supplied>πειτα καὶ ἐκδικίας τῆς προσηκού-

    <lb n="20"/>σης κατὰ τοὺς νόμους τυχεῖν. διευτύχει. 

    <lb n="21"/><choice><corr>ὑπατείας</corr><sic>υπατιας</sic></choice> τῶν δεσποτῶν ἡμῶν Λικινίου Σεβαστοῦ 

    <lb n="22"/>τὸ <num value="5">ε</num> καὶ Κρίσπου τοῦ <expan>ἐπιφανεστάτ<ex cert="high">ου</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">Καί</ex></expan>σαρος τὸ <num value="1">α</num>, <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Θὼθ</unclear> <num value="10"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear></num>. 

    <lb n="23"/><handShift new="m2"/> Αὐρήλιος Σακαῶν ἐπιδέδωκα. Αὐρήλιος 

    <lb n="24"/>Μάξιμος ἔγραψα <expan>ὑ<ex cert="high">πὲρ</ex></expan> αὐτοῦ ἀγραμμάτου. </ab></div><div n="meta.13057" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.13057" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="318" notBefore="318" type="textDate" value="0318-09-07">7. Sept. 318</date></p></div><div n="meta.13057" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Sakaon</title><biblScope type="numbers">39</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">13057</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0199</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">39</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0199;;39" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.13057" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">300</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">172</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.13057" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">P.Thead. pl. I</bibl><bibl type="illustration">Plate 8</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.13057" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">P.Thead. 21</bibl></div><div n="meta.13057" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Theadelphia</placeName> (<geogName cert="high" type="nome">Arsinoites</geogName>), <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div><div n="meta.13057" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DA